\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 21, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104xgf1665702831103.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xgf1665702831103.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xgf1665702831103.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"xgf1665702831103\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                          \n Define Tree Properties\n   </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Specify the structure and properties of a tree widget.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xgf1665702831103__p_d9377e1_d9378e1_d9379e1\">Use this dialog box to define the initial tree structure. To populate the tree with data at run time, you must define a ValRep list in the exec operation of the form on which this widget is painted.</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xgf1665702831103__section_eyx_1qk_5cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d840421e54\">Buttons</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"xgf1665702831103__ul_frj_bqk_5cc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xgf1665702831103__li_d4178e1_d4179e1_d4180e1\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Columns</span>—define the columns and\n          properties in the list view. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xgf1665702831103__li_d4181e1_d4182e1_d4183e1\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Types</span>—define tree item types in\n          the tree. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xgf1665702831103__li_d4184e1_d4185e1_d4186e1\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Structure</span>—define the location of\n          tree items in the tree hierarchy. Specify the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Build Tree Structure\n            By</span> property first. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xgf1665702831103__li_d4187e1_d4188e1_d4189e1\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">More</span>—specify additional\n          properties for this widget. </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xgf1665702831103__section_l4y_bqk_5cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d840421e86\">Properties</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"xgf1665702831103__ul_f4v_cqk_5cc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xgf1665702831103__li_d4190e1_d4191e1_d4192e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"kpu1665702635984.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kpu1665702635984.html\" title=\"Indicate the views displayed in the tree widget.\">Tree View and List View</a>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"xgf1665702831103__ul_h4v_cqk_5cc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xgf1665702831103__li_d4193e1_d4194e1_d4195e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"esw1665702635913.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/esw1665702635913.html\" title=\"Determines whether Expand (+) or Collapse (-) buttons are displayed in the Tree View. True (default) or False\">Collapse/Expand Buttons (HasButtons)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xgf1665702831103__li_d4196e1_d4197e1_d4198e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"iph1665702636198.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/iph1665702636198.html\" title=\"Determines whether lines are displayed between node and nodes, and node and leaves in the Tree View. True (default) or False.\">Node Lines (HasLines)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xgf1665702831103__li_d4199e1_d4200e1_d4201e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"fgn1665702636338.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fgn1665702636338.html\" title=\"Determines whether lines are displayed between first level of root tree items in the Tree View. True (default) or False.\">Root Lines (HasRootLines)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xgf1665702831103__li_d4202e1_d4203e1_d4204e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ztj1665702635769.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ztj1665702635769.html\" title=\"Determines whether the top level contents of a tree widget are expanded when it is first opened.\">Auto Expand (AutoExpand)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xgf1665702831103__li_d4205e1_d4206e1_d4207e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ylu1665702637742.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ylu1665702637742.html\" title=\"Enables (or disables) a delay of 200 milliseconds before firing the valueChanged trigger in the Tree widget, when using keyboard navigation.\">Selection Delay ( SelectionDelay)</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xgf1665702831103__li_d4208e1_d4209e1_d4210e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"qlx1665702636554.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qlx1665702636554.html\" title=\"Format of data is displayed in the List View.\">List View Style (ListView)</a>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"xgf1665702831103__ul_l4v_cqk_5cc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xgf1665702831103__li_d4211e1_d4212e1_d4213e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"upz1665702636480.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/upz1665702636480.html\" title=\"Specify whether the header should be displayed at the top of the List View:\">Show Header ( Header)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xgf1665702831103__li_d4214e1_d4215e1_d4216e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"bdf1665702635698.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bdf1665702635698.html\" title=\"Indicates whether sorting is allowed for the data columns in List View.\">Allow Sorting</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xgf1665702831103__li_d4217e1_d4218e1_d4219e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"hqk1665702636129.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hqk1665702636129.html\" title=\"Determines whether the user can select multiple items in the list view of the tree widget. True or False (default)\">MultiSelect ( ListMultiSelect)</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xgf1665702831103__li_d4220e1_d4221e1_d4222e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"lby1665702635845.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lby1665702635845.html\" title=\"Specify how the initial tree structure is built—using the id to link parent to child, or using numeric levels.\">Build Tree Structure By</a>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"xgf1665702831103__ul_o4v_cqk_5cc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xgf1665702831103__li_d4223e1_d4224e1_d4225e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"oth1665702636697.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/oth1665702636697.html\" title=\"Width of the pane that displays the Tree View in relation to the List View, expressed as a percentage of the total width.\">Width of Tree</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xgf1665702831103__li_d4226e1_d4227e1_d4228e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"qaj1665702636411.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qaj1665702636411.html\" title=\"String that separates selected tree items in the widget's field value when printing.\">Separation String</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xgf1665702831103__li_d4229e1_d4230e1_d4231e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"svg1665702629592.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/svg1665702629592.html\" title=\"Determines whether a border is displayed around the widget at run time. True or False. The default value depends on the widget.\">Frame</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xgf1665702831103__li_d4232e1_d4233e1_d4234e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"txj1665702628158.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/txj1665702628158.html\" title=\"This property determines whether a three-dimensional appearance is applied when the widget is displayed. True (default) or False.\">3-D Effect (3d)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xgf1665702831103__li_d4235e1_d4236e1_d4237e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"sew1665702635548.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/sew1665702635548.html\" title=\"Determines whether the user can edit text of the nodes and leafs in the tree widget at run time.\">Inline Edit ( InlineEdit)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xgf1665702831103__li_d4238e1_d4239e1_d4240e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"bou1665702610816.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bou1665702610816.html\" title=\"The Attach to Window Border (Attach) widget property attaches the widget (or area frame) to one or more form window borders or split bars at runtime. This allows the element to be resized or moved when the window is resized or a split bar moved.\">Attach to Window Border (attach)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xgf1665702831103__li_d4241e1_d4242e1_d4243e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rwc1665702587483.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rwc1665702587483.html\" title=\"Color to use as the background of the object.\">Background Color (BackColor)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xgf1665702831103__li_d4244e1_d4245e1_d4246e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rbp1665702587714.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rbp1665702587714.html\" title=\"Color to use as the foreground (usually the text color).\">Foreground Color (ForeColor)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xgf1665702831103__li_d4247e1_d4248e1_d4249e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"kfj1665702629663.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kfj1665702629663.html\" title=\"The Widget Font ( Font) property determines the font used to display the text in this widget.\">Widget Font ( Font)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xgf1665702831103__li_d4250e1_d4251e1_d4252e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"mdg1665702628370.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mdg1665702628370.html\" title=\"Font for the label associated with this widget. The specified label font is also used in widgets that support tool tip text. If not specified, the font definition in the application's .ini file is used.\">Label Font ( LabelFont)</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xgf1665702831103__section_gfs_dqk_5cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d840421e356\">How to</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"xgf1665702831103__ul_rln_2qk_5cc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xgf1665702831103__li_d4253e1_d4254e1_d4255e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"moy1665702638031.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/moy1665702638031.html\" title=\"A tree widget is useful for displaying and maintaining hierarchical information.\">Defining Tree Widgets</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xgf1665702831103__li_d4256e1_d4257e1_d4258e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"okv1665702558483.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/okv1665702558483.html\" title=\"The items listed in a tree widget typically represent a nested ValRep list. You can populate the initial list when defining the widget properties in the Component Editor. To make changes to the list, you must use ProcScript to update or rebuild the list.\">Defining and Updating ValRep Lists for the Tree Widget</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xgf1665702831103__li_d4259e1_d4260e1_d4261e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"aib1665702637820.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/aib1665702637820.html\" title=\"The initial tree structure that you define can be overridden at run time by data stored in database. You can activate operations in services to retrieve the relevant data and build the ValRep list dynamically.\">Dynamically Building the Tree Structure</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gge1665702634237.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>utree (Tree)</a><p>The utree widget enables users to view and navigate structured data as a hierarchy. Uniface provides a logical widget called Tree, which is mapped to utree.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533711\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533711\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Define Tree Properties Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 21, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Define Tree Properties Specify the structure and properties of a tree widget. Use this dialog box to define the initial tree structure. To populate the tree with data at run time, you must define a ValRep list in the exec operation of the form on which this widget is painted. Buttons Columns —define the columns and properties in the list view. Types —define tree item types in the tree. Structure —define the location of tree items in the tree hierarchy. Specify the Build Tree Structure By property first. More —specify additional properties for this widget. Properties Tree View and List View Collapse/Expand Buttons (HasButtons) Node Lines (HasLines) Root Lines (HasRootLines) Auto Expand (AutoExpand) Selection Delay ( SelectionDelay) List View Style (ListView) Show Header ( Header) Allow Sorting MultiSelect ( ListMultiSelect) Build Tree Structure By Width of Tree Separation String Frame 3-D Effect (3d) Inline Edit ( InlineEdit) Attach to Window Border (attach) Background Color (BackColor) Foreground Color (ForeColor) Widget Font ( Font) Label Font ( LabelFont) How to Defining Tree Widgets Defining and Updating ValRep Lists for the Tree Widget Dynamically Building the Tree Structure Related Links utree (Tree) The utree widget enables users to view and navigate structured data as a hierarchy. Uniface provides a logical widget called Tree, which is mapped to utree. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}